data.name: textBoxDescription.Text
data.value:
How to Use 1) Enter the message you want to spam in the "Message" box. 2) Open a chat window, eg. Steam chat or Skype. 3) Change speed with the sliding bar. Leftmost is faster, rightmost is slower. 4) Click "Start" and click on the chatbox. Warning: Don't click on ordinary windows, or else you might break something! 5) When you're done spamming, click "Stop" on the Solid Spammer window. 6) Watch as all of your friends block and remove you.
If you had to read all of this, then you're probably an idiot who shouldn't use this.
